      12-17 years with proper care. They are low-maintenance, requiring regular grooming and a balanced diet.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-box slide-on-scroll" id="about-box2">
    <p><span style="color: rgb(106, 202, 239); font-style: italic;">Siamese</span> is a sleek, elegant breed known for
